    <h1 class="opener__hed  -is-over-bg opener__hed--light opener__hed--small" >        This School for Autistic Youth Can Cost $573,200 a Year. It Operates With Little Oversight, and Students Have Suffered.
    </h1>

    
            <div class="article-meta-1  -is-over-bg article-meta-1--light">
            <span class="article-meta-1__byline">
                by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/jennifer-smith-richards">Jennifer Smith Richards</a> and <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/jodi-cohen">Jodi S. Cohen</a>            </span>
            <time class="article-meta-1__pubdate">
                <time class="timestamp" datetime="2024-05-08EDT06:00">May 8, 6 a.m. EDT</time>
            </time>
        </div>
    
