        <div class="content"> <!-- not sure if this is the best way to reestablish the text column -->
        <h2 class="opener__dek opener__dek--match-text-column" >            No state agency has authority over Shrub Oak, one of the country&#039;s most expensive therapeutic boarding schools. As a result, parents and staff have nowhere to report bruised students and medication mix-ups.
        </h2>
    </div>
    
</div>
        
