    <div class="story-card__description">
                
        <h3 class="story-card__hed" >
            <a href="https://www.propublica.org/getinvolved/help-propublica-report-on-education">
                                    Help ProPublica Report on Education
                            </a>
        </h3>

        <p class="story-card__dek" >
                            ProPublica is building a network of educators, students, parents and other experts to help guide our reporting about education. Take a few minutes to join our source network and share what you know.
                    </p>

        <p class="story-card__byline">
            by <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/ken-armstrong">Ken Armstrong</a>, <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/jennifer-berry-hawes">Jennifer Berry Hawes</a>, <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/nicole-carr">Nicole Carr</a>, <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/jodi-cohen">Jodi S. Cohen</a>, <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/asia-fields">Asia Fields</a>, <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/eli-hager">Eli Hager</a>, <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/alec-macgillis">Alec MacGillis</a>, <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/jeremy-schwartz">Jeremy Schwartz</a>, <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/jennifer-smith-richards">Jennifer Smith Richards</a> and <a class="name" href="https://www.propublica.org/people/aliyya-swaby">Aliyya Swaby</a>,             <time class="timestamp" datetime="2024-03-11EDT12:00">March 11, 12 p.m. EDT</time>
        </p>

            </div>
</div>
            </ul>
</div>



    
